Package com.example.flexiMed.model

Class ServiceHistoryEntity

java.lang.Object
com.example.flexiMed.model.ServiceHistoryEntity
@Entity public class ServiceHistoryEntity extends Object
Entity representing the service history for a request in the system. This entity tracks the events associated with a request, such as updates or status changes.
